    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h2 id=\"HoldoutsinMaya-EnablingHoldoutsinMaya\">Enabling Holdouts in Maya</h2><p>Holdouts can be enabled by selecting holdout geometry and clicking the <strong>Holdout</strong> button in the RenderMan shelf.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543095/holdoutbutton.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431592342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543095/holdoutbutton.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431592342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544543117\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"holdoutbutton.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544543095\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e4f18f11-81ee-47ef-8a5b-bf0ad6259462\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p>This has two effects. It enables the selected shape's <strong>Hold-Out</strong> attribute:</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543095/holdoutattr.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431592342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543095/holdoutattr.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431592342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544543114\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"holdoutattr.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544543095\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"dd38900a-af66-4576-a54d-44e741fb18ef\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p>It also enables the <strong>Output Shadow AOV</strong> option under the Advanced render settings:</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543095/holdout-matte-render-settings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431592342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544543095/holdout-matte-render-settings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431592342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544543111\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"holdout-matte-render-settings.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544543095\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"afae95c9-b2a4-4a30-823d-456a8fbce6fe\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p>Holdouts can be visualized in Maya using <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544541707/Cameras+in+Maya#CamerasinMaya-ImagePlanes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541707\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">image planes</a> with the <strong>Image Plane As Sample Filter</strong> Advanced render setting enabled.  This setting is enabled by default.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"2ea501b1-3527-43e8-9dcf-98a0fbc2931d\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>To turn off the Holdout AOVs (prevent output) you can choose &quot;None&quot; in the &quot;Output Shadow AOV&quot; as noted above.</p></div></div><p><br/></p><h2 id=\"HoldoutsinMaya-AboutHoldouts\">About Holdouts</h2><p><div class=\"contentLayout2 conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-macro-id=\"3b009dd9-0839-47c2-a2c0-662857bf6b33\" data-macro-name=\"include\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/holdouts.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1693958601770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/holdouts.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1693958601770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"450\" data-width=\"731\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673947\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"holdouts.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"99bb59c4-e313-490f-acbe-2ad815725b8c\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><p><br /></p><p>VFX artists often need to composite the CG objects over a live action film plate. To convince the audience that the CG objects are real and belong to the scene, holdouts are used to collect the CG objects' shadow and reflection that match very closely to the shadow and reflection in the live action plate.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"holdouts0.png\" width=\"365\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/holdouts0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908235433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=365&amp;height=225\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/holdouts0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908235433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"225\" data-width=\"365\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673926\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"holdouts0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"6bed2239-701e-42c4-acc7-4f8746f8fca3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/holdouts0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908235433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=365&amp;height=225 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/holdouts0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908235433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=365&amp;height=225 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"holdouts1.png\" width=\"365\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/holdouts1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908244334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=365&amp;height=225\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/holdouts1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908244334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"225\" data-width=\"365\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673923\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"holdouts1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"a1978d56-d768-457b-aad5-662fee93285d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/holdouts1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908244334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=365&amp;height=225 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/holdouts1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908244334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=365&amp;height=225 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h2 id=\"HoldoutsinMaya-Geometry\">Geometry</h2><p>Holdout objects are used in place of real world object to catch light interactions from 3D objects. In RenderMan, holdout objects are specified by enabling the <strong>trace</strong> <strong>holdout</strong> attribute.</p><div class=\"code panel pdl conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"a26a5d2a-57e7-4c21-a33e-c98c0345cc52\" data-macro-name=\"code\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"codeContent panelContent pdl\">\n<pre class=\"syntaxhighlighter-pre\" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=\"brush: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence\" data-theme=\"Confluence\">Attribute &quot;trace&quot; &quot;int holdout&quot; [1]</pre>\n</div></div><h2 id=\"HoldoutsinMaya-IntegratorsandAOVs\">Integrators and AOVs</h2><p>Holdouts are an illumination feature implemented at the integrator level. They are able to catch a variety of integrator-specific illumination effects such as diffuse and specular reflections, transmissions, and caustics. Available integrator that support holdouts are: <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661775/PxrPathTracer\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661775\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrPathTracer</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661785/PxrVCM\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661785\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrVCM</a>, and PxrUnified.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"integrator0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/integrator0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908279741&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/integrator0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908279741&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673953\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"integrator0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"02f4736a-7ffa-4725-a524-abd449920e5a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/integrator0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908279741&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/integrator0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908279741&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"integrator1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/integrator1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908285171&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/integrator1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908285171&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673950\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"integrator1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"4ac86bf2-e767-477d-a4d9-c21804cfe8cb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/integrator1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908285171&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/integrator1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908285171&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>LPE workflow remains unchanged for holdout geometry.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"aovs0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908336900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/aovs0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908336900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673962\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"aovs0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"f0ca43f0-2960-4360-8021-ff67a3b78048\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908336900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908336900&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"aovs1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908340393&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/aovs1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908340393&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673959\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"aovs1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"2ef49792-0ae3-4d48-b185-7c8b1d030d5d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908340393&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908340393&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"aovs2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908345774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/aovs2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908345774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673956\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"aovs2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"0a70af41-0962-4751-b8d2-c302883beae8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908345774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/aovs2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908345774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"671895f4-614d-480b-8f1c-49c1ce481b01\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Because holdouts workflow involves multiple AOVs, rendering with <strong>adapt all</strong> enabled can reduce noise at the cost of slower speed as it may trigger more samples based on noisier AOVs.</p></div></div><h2 id=\"HoldoutsinMaya-Lights\">Lights</h2><p>By default, light sources are considered holdouts and do not illuminate other holdout objects directly. This prevents double contribution between lights used to illuminate non-holdout geometry and the illumination already captured on the plate image.</p><p>To create a light source that does directly illuminate holdout objects, use <em>&quot;__illumholdout&quot;</em> as the light group suffix. This tells integrator plug-ins to consider this light as a non-holdout light source when determining illumination.</p><div class=\"code panel pdl conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"ccad30d4-b64e-41ba-ac87-8896867baa7a\" data-macro-name=\"code\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"codeContent panelContent pdl\">\n<pre class=\"syntaxhighlighter-pre\" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=\"brush: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence\" data-theme=\"Confluence\">Light &quot;PxrSphereLight&quot; &quot;spherelight&quot; &quot;string lightGroup&quot; [&quot;light__illumholdout&quot;]</pre>\n</div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"illumholdout0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/illumholdout0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908382847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/illumholdout0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908382847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673932\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"illumholdout0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"bc2b0fd8-69f8-4dda-b837-1a0449dbaf59\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/illumholdout0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908382847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/illumholdout0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908382847&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"illumholdout1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/illumholdout1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908387614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/illumholdout1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908387614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673929\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"illumholdout1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"7b54853e-ee9b-4d05-8b88-25e6f86202e8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/illumholdout1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908387614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/illumholdout1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908387614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h2 id=\"HoldoutsinMaya-Alpha,Shadows,andCompositing\">Alpha, Shadows, and Compositing</h2><p>Holdout contribution can be composited over a film plate using an alpha and shadow pass as masks. The shadow pass is generated using the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662371/PxrShadowDisplayFilter\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662371\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrShadowDisplayFilter</a> plug-in and can be optionally written to its own AOV or added to the alpha. The occluded and unoccluded input AOVs should be rendered using the <strong>holdouts</strong> LPE prefix so that they only contain the shadowing term for holdout geometry.</p><div class=\"code panel pdl conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"4e6c8b9b-b877-4997-a83e-495e0903833e\" data-macro-name=\"code\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"codeContent panelContent pdl\">\n<pre class=\"syntaxhighlighter-pre\" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=\"brush: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence\" data-theme=\"Confluence\">DisplayChannel &quot;color shadow&quot;\nDisplayChannel &quot;color occluded&quot; &quot;string source&quot; [&quot;color lpe:holdouts;C[DS]+[LO]&quot;]\nDisplayChannel &quot;color unoccluded&quot; &quot;string source&quot; [&quot;color lpe:holdouts;unoccluded;C[DS]+[LO]&quot;]</pre>\n</div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"mask0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908423021&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/mask0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908423021&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673938\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mask0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"0f069993-c4e5-4be3-9d54-a13a92d1d4a9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908423021&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908423021&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"mask1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908431341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/mask1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908431341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673935\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mask1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"e578ce64-a2ec-47a9-988a-1f3860b914d8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908431341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908431341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"mask2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908440065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/mask2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908440065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673920\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"mask2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"30c2545d-a7e3-4a81-8e2a-f5edfc8c5e18\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908440065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/mask2.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908440065&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Compositing can be interactively previewed in RenderMan by using the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661891/PxrImageDisplayFilter\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661891\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrImageDisplayFilter</a> plug-in. This will composite the film plate with the beauty channel, using the alpha channel and holdout shadow AOV to mask the plate.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"imageplane0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/imageplane0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908466387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/imageplane0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908466387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673944\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"imageplane0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"ae1c5835-17a5-4254-922c-599236bb9a73\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/imageplane0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908466387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/imageplane0.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908466387&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"imageplane1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/imageplane1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908470634&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/imageplane1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908470634&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19673941\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"imageplane1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"19661827\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"6938dd60-a160-43cf-bdd5-5111c07c95ae\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/imageplane1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908470634&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/19661827/imageplane1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1718908470634&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h2 id=\"HoldoutsinMaya-CompositingWorkflow\">Compositing Workflow</h2><p>When compositing the image if the shadow matte is part of the beauty, it is a simple over operation. This will provide you with the correct shadow density and look based on the render settings.</p><p>However, this means adjusting the shadow density is tied to your beauty alpha, you will need a mask to prevent shadow adjustments from ruining your CG object composite. Cryptomatte may handle this for you as part of your usual arsenal.</p><p>If you output the shadow matte separately then you can adjust the shadow density separately, however you may have a coverage issue, the solution is to merge your alphas together in comp from the beauty and the shadow matte. An example using Nuke is <a href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/19661827/holdout_NukeScript.zip?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1693958602131&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></p>"
    }
